      Splash SVG total duration: 5s
      Sequence (all SMIL, one clock):
        arc2 draws:   0   -> 18%  (0.0s - 0.9s)
        n2 lights:    18% -> 28%  (0.9s - 1.4s)
        arc1 draws:   26% -> 44%  (1.3s - 2.2s)
        n3 lights:    44% -> 52%  (2.2s - 2.6s)
        arc3 draws:   52% -> 70%  (2.6s - 3.5s)
        center lights:70% -> 90%  (3.5s - 4.5s)
        letters fade: 70% -> 90%  (3.5s - 4.5s)  <-- same window as center
    -->
    <div id="splash">
      <div id="splash-logo">
